{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "失路人", "storyInfo": "葬禮過後，幫助過拉芙希妮的“放逐王”再度現身，邀請她隨自己見證王城遺跡深處的秘密。在那裡，拉芙希妮直面塔拉歷史覆轍的同時，也見證了“放逐王”自己的故事。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，即便去城裡不為別的，只為舉行一場還火儀式，你們仍然不願意嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您所述的情況實在太過反常。僅憑您的言語，我們也無法確認城中居民的生與死。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不要說還火儀式只是葬禮罷了，請您不要抱不切實際的期望。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那就請回吧，守靈人。無論如何，感謝你們的幫助。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便沒有我們，您也要回去納斯爾紗？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭他們如今融入得很好，我沒什麼好擔心的，涅梅絲的託付也完成了……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經沒有其他該做的事了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍閣下，請保重。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會的。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍邁步，獨自向來時的方向繼續前進。昨日種種，留到眼中僅餘一簇微弱的影。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那同樣也是一簇小小的火。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“還火”……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下定決心回去送死了？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知名的先生？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您來得剛剛好，我們得談一談。如果您願意幫我——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有在你的紅龍歷史課上，聽過一個叫拉布雷德的倒楣鬼的故事？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——先生？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，看來你沒有。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出走多年以後第一次回到王城，還沒見到他親愛的胞弟，就被護衛領走，被利劍穿胸而死……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我知道這段故事。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也打算學他，當一個徹徹底底的蠢貨，是嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧。你見到了你姐姐，人到現在也都還活著，已經比倒楣鬼好太多了，是不是？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#12$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉布雷德和艾里爾的故事，並不是我和愛布拉娜的故事。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼，就當作是我偏要把閒事管到底吧。你剛才不是想跟我談談嗎？要談什麼？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡的還火儀式。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來只想多找一個準備儀式的人，但您看起來很瞭解塔拉的歷史掌故，我想，也許您能為我提供一些幫助……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史？掌故？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們不如邊走邊聊。走這邊。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是黑林在那邊——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我走，就像在黑林裡那次一樣，聽到了嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g7_galekingruins", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……王城的遺址？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經來過這裡。這裡的源石多發環境並不安全——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是要歷史和掌故嗎？找遍整個塔拉，還有哪個地方能比得上這座*古老的廷蓋語粗口*王城？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座什麼樣的王城？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呿，沒什麼。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我始終感激那時您在黑林提供的幫助，但現在我的確也有更重要的事，沒有太多時間——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼事？送死？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和你姐姐還真是大不相同。那條紅龍的火焰受了詛咒，性格卻典型到不行，目空一切，聽不見其他聲音。你就不一樣了——", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和姐姐原本就不同，但她也並不是您說的這樣。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論你們如何不同，紅龍的天性都是鬥爭，即使你只是被捲入的那個也一樣。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而鬥爭從來都只有一種結果，你死，或是她亡。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以說，反正有一個人要死，為什麼要這麼急呢？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多一點耐心吧，年輕人。我們就快到了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們今天來這裡就是為了這個祭台。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祭台？您是說中間的那個嗎？但那個不是……熔爐嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“熔融了所有塔拉戰士的武器、顛覆了王朝命運的熔爐”……令死去的戰士從中復生的熔爐。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，現在你們都這麼稱呼它？神秘兮兮的，聽起來反而比“祭台”厲害許多。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但很可惜，祭台就是祭台，只不過比其他祭台龐大。王城的核心就圍著它建立，蓋爾王加冕時的儀式石陣即是它的前身。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而老紅龍死去的時候，人們也會在這裡為他還火。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還火？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就跟你在那群木頭腦袋那裡看見的東西一樣。這麼多年了，他們還真是一直記得清清楚楚。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在那個年代的還火並不是點起篝火就好了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅里亞德那老女人的時候，繼承蓋爾王之位的紅龍的兄弟姐妹，只要把手伸進火裡燙幾個泡就結束了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過再往上追溯，據說，只是據說，很久很久以前，那些兄弟姐妹都要一起在火裡殉葬。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，你的臉色越來越糟了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他揚起手，一簇紫火從他的袖口匯入祭台中跳動著的、同樣是紫色的火苗。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火焰安穩地呼吸，彷彿嬰孩卧在母親的襁褓之中。"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的火也是紫色？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，您是德拉克……難道您是——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯獨在這件事上你顯得異常遲鈍，但現在你已經逃不掉了。把手放進來。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是想讓納斯爾紗還火嗎？想，就把手放進來。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍於是沉默。她伸出手，觸碰熔爐中的火苗——那火一如既往地並不溫暖，卻也出乎意料地算不上冰冷。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我能告訴你，帶你來這裡，是為讓你看清——", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉如今的悲劇，紅龍長久以來的污名……一切不過始於重蹈命運殘忍的覆轍。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和你的好姐姐同為噴吐死火的異種，而我現在已經不願，也無法再對死者有分毫不敬，不過是帶你看看在這片土地上死去的人……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的命運罷了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "fire"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "channel": "fire", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_deathburning", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "要從這裡開始嗎？這算是最近頭一樁大事了，也可以理解。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你那個好姐姐是對的。沾上了死火的東西無藥可救，只是這道火本來不該這麼容易蔓延。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我倒一直好奇，究竟是多大的怨恨，才能讓德拉克六百年後再次誕下不祥的異種？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "哦，然後是他。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "要我說，他醒得太晚了，太陽都要下山了，他才從床上爬起來，只能理所當然地淪為犧牲品。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……即使是您，也請不要這樣輕描淡寫地帶過死亡，不要用犧牲的名義將它合理化。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那也許只是因為你見的還不夠多。要是習慣了，忍一忍就過去了——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "看，另一個犧牲品來了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死你的維多利亞人，他們已經被趕走了！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連最後那個維多利亞壞種，也已經在我眼前……死掉了……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不得不說，你姐姐的願景在某種意義上的確化為現實了。塔拉人站起，維多利亞人倒下。簡單、直接、“大快人心”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您也是……袖手旁觀的其中一員？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "別鑽牛角尖了，小鬼。都到這個份上了，你知道我是什麼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "58_mini01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我從未見過這種場面，幫我介紹一下？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是一場戰爭。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "戰爭不計其數，你得說得更明白點。她燒死的是哪家仇敵，目光望向的又是哪片土地？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞。愛布拉娜要將塔拉的權柄自阿斯蘭手中奪回。這就是那場戰爭的尾聲。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "阿斯蘭？那夥自詡與眾不同的混蛋？但她面對的難道不是薩卡茲嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "算了。原來是獅子搶走了維多利亞，我知道這一點就夠了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I5", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "就算你不說，我也知道這是什麼。就像即使被面具遮蓋，我也猜得到那下面的表情。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只有在面對已成定局的死亡時，紅龍臉上才會出現的……得償所願的滿足與狂喜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……那不是喜悅，那是和喜悅背道而馳的——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "背道而馳？應該不是那時你受的傷太過嚴重，已經開始在臨死前美化看見的一切了吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我說過了，這不過是重蹈覆轍，城市騎上了輪子，國度更換了主人，但內部的東西毫無二致。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i11", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這是哪裡？是你們的家嗎？是你們學著怎樣對彼此刀劍相向的地方？這個人又是誰？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃里克伯爵，我與愛布拉娜的收養者。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜說他使塔拉人看到了希望，能看見，卻永遠無法抵達，將渴水的旅人用幻景逼入瘋癲。這就是他所做的一切。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他手握那條纖細的絲線，而絲線連接的兩端，一邊是終於找回名姓的塔拉人，一邊是長久立於上位的壓迫者。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那條線就是姐姐和我。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在想來……他或許正是第一個身染紫火之人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "fire", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "fire"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不僅同情你姐姐，而且還相當理解她。怪不得你不願殺死她。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我絕不會成為她，也不會選擇引頸就戮。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g14_galekingruins_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您讓我回溯這一連串的事件，或者說歷史，究竟想向我證明什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "證明塔拉的歷史就是舊日廢墟的不斷堆疊與組合，你見過的東西，我也已經見過，從中已經無法發掘出任何新的事物。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我看到的不是廢墟，而是……火焰的根源。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "納斯爾紗城內的火確實是姐姐的火，但也同樣是那些血腥背後，龐大而無處安放的悲傷。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是戰爭……不，是從戰爭開始前早就出現的那些痛苦、那些壓迫、那些被奪走的東西，點燃了人們心中的火。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在姐姐的塑造之下，那些悲傷化為仇恨，燒遍了塔拉的原野，趕走了維多利亞人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了現在，悲傷已經無從以復仇掩蓋，於是那道火只好燒灼人們自己，將他們燃盡，成為一具又一具行屍走肉。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯的總結，小鬼，但你真覺得，只是一場還火，就能解決城裡的一切嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我面前只有這一條路。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，但這條路到底該如何踏上去呢？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過來。你的事看完了，還有我的呢。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_R1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）別哭，別哭了。不就是一隻雲獸嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）可是灰爪是我從小養到大的……", "name": "傷心的女孩"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）爸爸，人們都說你的火焰不一樣，你不能醫治活著的人，卻能讓死去的人回來……", "name": "傷心的女孩"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）那不是回來，那只是空殼。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）就算是空殼也好，爸爸，求你了，我只想再聽聽灰爪的叫聲……", "name": "傷心的女孩"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "性情衝動的紅龍就這樣敗在小女兒的請求之下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "於是，數月之後，不僅雲獸，整片牧場的獸群都出現異象。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "馱獸不吃草，瘤獸不產奶，老去的遲遲不死，新生的頻頻夭折，甚至還有剃光肉的骨架在草場上徘徊……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "紫火在獸群間蔓延，紅龍不得不帶著族人離開那片牧場。在他不算太長的一生中，這樣的錯誤，他犯過許多次。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紫火……沾染獸群？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "獸群又怎樣？你的好姐姐竟敢用這道火去燒灼死去的人，這才真正叫人瞠目結舌。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這道火焰最終到底是怎樣熄滅的？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……接下來，你會知道的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g12_castlecorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是……納斯爾紗的堡壘？那條長廊？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "錯，但錯不在你。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們只是向過去跨了一大步，這就是你腳下的王城……六百多年前的樣子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "幾百年後的石匠能將王城原有的樣子搬上你們所謂的“納斯爾紗”，這是唯一讓我嚇了一跳的事情。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡……發生了什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這裡……哈……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愚蠢的拉布雷德犯了太多次你見過的錯誤，他逐漸變得虛弱，覺得自己大限將至。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，在夏末節前夕，他臨時起意，帶著遊牧生活能讓他備好的最上等的禮物，只為了見闊別二十年的弟弟一面。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他甚至說動了城中掌管祭典儀式的祭司們，讓他們向弟弟引見自己。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祭司們被他的思念之情打動，帶他進入城中，然而不知何時起，帶他的人的聲音、身形、態度，好像全變了。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接著，他被帶到這條長廊——"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_battlepresent", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 45.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜下令誅殺兄長的艾里爾並不在大門另一邊的陽台上，因為就算我到死也睜著眼，還是沒能從那條縫隙之中瞧見他的火。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "究竟是哪裡出了差錯？"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是城中祭司仍以對待王族的態度待我便使他慍怒，還是我一聲不響二十餘年的遠離早已令他深覺背叛？"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者……想要殺死我的另有其人，他只是不得不照做？"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無從知曉。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這場短暫而迅速的圍殺中，唯有一件事是我早已瞭解且深信不疑的——"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍永不原諒。紅龍的恨意比塔拉的歷史更長。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g14_galekingruins_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我要告訴你的還不只這些。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我死後，艾里爾指使手下在王城中拖行我的棺槨，向每個人展示我的下場。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，每一處我曾帶族人停留過的牧場都燃起熊熊紫火，凡是沾染那道火的，生命無不背棄，只留死亡佔據。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "七日之後，祭司們在黑林外一處曠野上為我還火，直到他們還給我的火焰熄滅，牧場上的紫火才緩緩退去。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是到那個時候，我死後一直在火中殘存的那點意識才徹底沒入黑暗。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那些沾染了火的生靈，無論野獸還是人類……統統化為灰燼。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$2"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你姐姐沒有騙你。她不死，這道火焰只會繼續蔓延下去。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#9$2"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，她又是一條極度典型的紅龍，她才不會高尚到為了拯救那些還沒活下來的人丟掉性命。她讓你回去，其中不可能沒有陷阱。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，跑，去求助，去呼喊，去讓與她旗鼓相當的對手撲滅這些不知會蔓延到何時的火，這就是你唯一的辦法。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果她已經認定，只有我有資格當她旗鼓相當的舞伴呢？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果我只是無法放著那一城或許還有救的生命不管呢？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你就要去幫一個活著的人還火？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那要是幫活人還火沒用呢？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$2"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我都會回去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#12$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "良久，拉芙希妮只聽見一聲嘆息。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）愚蠢和倔強還真是代代相傳。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$2"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}